Maria A. TORRES, Plaintiff-Appellant v. CITY OF SAN ANTONIO, Defendant-Appellee. No. 05-50458. United States Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. May 3, 2007. Russell J.G. Amsberry, Law Offices of Russell Amsberry, San Antonio, TX, for Plaintiff-Appellant. Shawn Kevin Fitzpatrick, San Antonio, TX, for Defendant-Appellee.

Before KING, DAVIS, and BARKSDALE, Circuit Judges.

*336PER CURIAM: *

AFFIRMED. See 5th Circuit Loc. R. 47.6.

Pursuant to 5th Cir. R. 47.5, the Court has determined that this opinion should not be published and is not precedent except under the limited circumstances set forth in 5th Cir. R. 47.5.4.
